1445
01:16:37,176 --> 01:16:41,722
Yes, yeah, yeah, I think, Harriet Tubman
had the number three...

1446
01:16:42,348 --> 01:16:43,599
John Clancy...

1447
01:16:46,185 --> 01:16:47,895
any man with that attention to detail

1448
01:16:48,604 --> 01:16:50,815
