01:16:52,983 --> 01:16:56,946
Well, thank you, thank you, Richard,
you won't be disappointed.

1451
01:16:57,029 --> 01:16:58,531
You keep those ribs comin',

1452
01:16:58,781 --> 01:17:01,534
